data.name: Verdant Tidecaller
data.rulesText:
Whenever a land enters the battlefield under your control, you may pay 1. If you do, create a 1/1 green Saproling creature token.
Pay {G} {G}: Return target land card from your graveyard to your hand.
data.flavorText: "The forest remembers its own, and the earth answers its call."
data.pwDesc1: Create a 1/1 black Zombie creature token with deathtouch.
data.pwDesc2: Up to one target creature gets -X/-X until your next turn, where X is the number of Zombies you control.
data.pwDesc3: Exile all creature cards from graveyards. For each card exiled this way, create a 2/2 black Zombie creature token.
